# Canonical ignore file for codebase-maintenance scans.
#
# Patterns before any `context` line apply to every scan root.
# Patterns after `context <working-directory>` apply only when the directory
# passed to find_large_files.py matches that working-directory suffix or glob.
#
# Ignore patterns are relative to the scan root.
# - `cache/` ignores any directory named `cache` at any depth.
# - `*.generated.ts` ignores matching files anywhere in the scan.
# - `*/__pycache__` ignores matching directories via glob.
#
# Example:
# context */pi-config/
# analysis/data/exports/
# *.generated.ts

node_modules/
out/
.vscode-test/
coverage/
*.min.js
*.bundle.*
*.chunk.*
*.generated.*
*.pb.*
*_pb2.py
*_pb2_grpc.py
